            n
          
        
        
          x
          
            m
          
        
        
          y
          
            n
          
        
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle G(a_{m,n};x,y)=\sum _{m,n=0}^{\infty }a_{m,n}x^{m}y^{n}.}
  


=== Exponential generating function (EGF) ===
The exponential generating function of a sequence an is

  
    
      
        EG
        ⁡
