          n
          
            2
          
        
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle a_{n}\sim {\frac {B(r)}{r^{\alpha }\Gamma (\beta )}}\,n^{\beta -1}\left({\frac {1}{r}}\right)^{n}={\frac {1(1+1)}{1^{0}\,\Gamma (3)}}\,n^{3-1}(1/1)^{n}=n^{2}.}
  


