                  −
                  4
                  x
                
              
            
            
              2
              x
            
          
        
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\frac {1-{\sqrt {1-4x}}}{2x}}.}
  With r = 1/4, α = 1, β = −1/2, A(x) = 1/2, and B(x) = −1/2, we can conclude that, for the Catalan numbers,

  
    
      
        
          a
          
