          ∑
          
            n
            ≥
            0
          
        
        
          (
          n
          +
          1
          )
          
            z
            
              n
            
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\frac {1}{(1-z)^{2}}}=\sum _{n\geq 0}{(n+1)z^{n}}}
  , convolution with the numerator yields

  
    
      
        
          s
          
            n
          
        
        =
        
          ∑
          
            k
            =
            1
          
          
