        <
        2
        p
      
    
    {\displaystyle 0\leq n<2p}
  . Then 1) the function 
  
    
      
        
          A
          
            p
          
        
        (
        z
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle A_{p}(z)}
   is rational for all 
  
    
      
        p
        ≥
        2
      
    
    {\displaystyle p\geq 2}
   where we assume that one of divisibility criteria of 
  
    
      
        p
        
          |
        
        
          p
          
            1
          
        
        ,
        
          p
          
            1
          
        
        
