        x
        +
        1
        
          )
          
            ⌊
            n
            
              /
            
            2
            ⌋
          
        
        ,
      
    
    {\displaystyle S_{n}(x)=[x(x+1)]\cdot [x(x+1)]\cdots =x^{\lceil n/2\rceil }(x+1)^{\lfloor n/2\rfloor },}
  which implies that the parity of these Stirling numbers matches that of the binomial coefficient

  
    
      
        
          [
          
            
              
                
                  n
                
              
              
                
