    {\displaystyle F(z)^{x}=\exp \left(x\log F(z)\right)=\sum _{n\geq 0}f_{n}(x)z^{n},}
  for some analytic function 
  
    
      
        F
      
    
    {\displaystyle F}
   with a power series expansion such that 
  
    
      
        F
        (
        0
        )
        =
        1
      
    
    {\displaystyle F(0)=1}
  . 
We say that a family of polynomials, 
  
    
      
        
          f
          
